{"tid":415912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反星英雄】余澎杉確認獲美政治庇護　聲言續批星加坡政府","createTime":"2017-09-27T11:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T11:17:55.000Z","uid":37661,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89d4ade2476dcb6d182a3448e7844f593b2c71f4","tid":415912,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"方潤南報道<br />\n<br />\n美國移民上訴委員會，維持給予星加坡青年余澎杉政治庇護的決定，他即時獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n曾經在網上批評已故前總理李光耀和星加坡政府的余澎杉，被星加坡法院兩度判監，去年12月到美國尋求政治庇護，其後獲批，但國土安全部提出上訴，他一直被收押。上訴委員會認同，假如他返回星加坡，會受到逼害。<br />\n<br />\n重獲自由的余澎杉說，終於可以暢所欲言，日後會繼續批評星加坡政府。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1356232_1_20170927165223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1356232_1_20170927165223.jpg&h=7424c734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1356232-20170927.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1356232-20170927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=t1bT9n%2B3oRbgiqcc%2BMDm6viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=71c775f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1356232-20170927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=35792377\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1356232-20170927.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}